genresAdvancedInfo.name: cumbia cristiana
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Cumbia cristiana is a subgenre of Latin American music that fuses traditional cumbia rhythms with Christian lyrics. The music is often characterized by its upbeat tempo, use of accordion and percussion instruments, and catchy melodies. The lyrics typically focus on themes of faith, hope, and love, and aim to spread a positive message to listeners. Popular artists in this genre include
